                    </h1>                  

                </div>

                <div class="extra-list">
                    <ul data-bullet="primary">
                        <li>Entyvio works through a gut-selective MOA by specifically binding to the &alpha;4&beta;7 integrin and blocking its interaction with MAdCAM-1, which is mainly expressed on gut endothelial cells.<sup>1-7</sup></li>
                        <li>Remission was evaluated at Week 52.<sup>1</sup> Individual results may vary.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </article>
